label: A3B5_tI32_108_ac_a2c-001
title: Sr$_{5}$Si$_{3}$ Structure ({\em Obsolete})
comments:
This is the original determination of the Sr$_{5}$Si$_{3}$ (Nagorsen, 1967). Later(Nesper, 1999) re-examined the system and found that it is actually in the \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B5_tI32_140_ah_cl-001}{$D8_{l}$ Cr$_{5}$B$_{3}$ structure}, space group $I4/mcm$ \#140. 
 We include this here as our first example of a structure in space group $I4cm$ \#108.
